import{_ as t,c as o,b as a,o as i}from"./chunks/framework.Bh4f_7Kc.js";const f=JSON.parse('{"title":"","description":"","frontmatter":{},"headers":[],"relativePath":"guide/Washington.md","filePath":"guide/Washington.md"}'),n={name:"guide/Washington.md"};function p(s,e,r,h,l,d){return i(),o("div",null,e[0]||(e[0]=[a("<p>Yue Yizheng&#39;s friendship is a slow-growing plant. It must go through hardships to withstand the impact of adversity. Only then can it be worthy of the title of friendship.</p><p>---002---</p><p>You cannot defeat your master and establish harmony with the people. Don&#39;t just promise to others easily. Once you promise to others, you must keep your promise.</p><p>---003---</p><p>The correct standard to measure the quality of a friend is to use it for positive purposes rather than using words.</p><p>---004---</p><p>If you value your reputation and still use it, you should go to the country and associate with virtuous people; if you are known to others as a lowly person and inferior to them, it is better for you to live in seclusion.</p><p>---005---</p><p>Yue Yizhen&#39;s friendship is a slow-growing plant.</p><p>---006---</p><p>Look more closely at the past and see that spark of conscience in your heart will never go out.</p><p>---007---</p><p>Why would a government have the power to prohibit free speech? There are only three explanations:</p><ol><li><p>It used to be a little bit shy and was afraid people would mention it.</p></li><li><p>It is doing bad things to make people feel good and afraid of being criticized;</p></li><li><p>It is preparing to do something bad to Sheng Li Renhe, but is afraid that people will expose it.</p></li></ol><p>I have always believed that banning speech must be related to bad voices and harmony, and definitely not good voices and harmony.</p><p>---008---</p><p>Once freedom takes root, it will grow rapidly like a plant.</p><p>---009---</p><p>除了我们自己以地会地，都声立有人能贬低我们。如果我们坚强，走物把都声立有甚么不良影响能够以们眼败我们。</p><p>---010---</p><p>All harmony and balance, health and fitness, success and happiness are naturally generated and created by optimism and hope.</p><p>---011---</p><p>我希望我得觉具有足够的坚定性和美德，藉以保持所有称号中，我好再为最值得羡慕的称号：一个诚走物的人。</p><p>---012---</p><p>The standard for measuring the quality of friends is to use positive things instead of words; those who only say good things on the surface but actually deviate from this standard are the ones who set the stage for improvement.</p><p>---013---</p><p>If the books you read cannot be used for national purposes, then the books you read are just waste paper.</p><p>---014---</p><p>My observation is that when you use a certain task alone, it can be done by one person... but it will be much worse when you use it alone, and I feel that when you use more people, you almost always have to do something.</p><p>---015---</p><p>When you are a student, you can only do meaningful things, but not go astray.</p><p>---016---</p><p>Skeptics are society&#39;s too much of a pushover.</p><p>---017---</p><p>I always think that the sword is our last resort to defend our freedom, and it is also the first means by which we gain freedom.</p><p>---018---</p><p>Our first generation focused on development, the second generation focused on construction, and the third generation felt that our generation could achieve success in literature, architecture, and art.</p><p>---019---</p><p>labor to keep alive in your breast that little spark of celestial fire, called conscience.</p><p>The efforts made to keep the sacred fire burning in the heart will have a great impact on the conscience of the outside world.</p><p>---020---</p><p>If you cannot defeat your master and establish harmony with the people, you should never just say one thing to another easily; since you have made a promise, you must fulfill your promise.</p><p>---021---</p><p>If you help people get what they want, you can get everything you want.</p><p>---022---</p><p>If you can&#39;t use what you read, then what you read is just like waste paper.</p><p>---023---</p><p>&quot;If freedom of speech is denied to us, we will be made dumb and silent, like sheep that will soon be slaughtered.&quot;</p><p>---024---</p><p>No matter what family rules are used to gain reputation, if there is no character to support it in front of it, the reputation will eventually disappear.</p><p>---025---</p><p>The scientific and cultural achievements of the public are far more worthy of our support. In a country, knowledge is the most solid foundation for the public to obtain happiness.</p><p>---026---</p><p>If freedom is allowed to flow freely, the devil of despotism will take the opportunity to invade.</p><p>---027---</p><p>My wife is the most beautiful woman I have ever seen. I owe everything I have to my wife. All the success I have in my life I owe to the moral, intellectual and physical education I received from her.</p><p>---028---</p><p>Try to look at the past Lord and see that the spark of conscience in your heart will never be extinguished.</p><p>---029---</p><p>Let your heart feel for the affliction and distress of everyone</p><p>Go to the Lord and see your lower ten hearts and feel the pain and misfortune of the people</p><p>---030---</p><p>In all nations, knowledge is the most reliable foundation of public happiness.</p><p>---031---</p><p>I hope I have enough firmness and virtue to retain for myself the most enviable of all titles: that of a man of integrity.</p><p>---032---</p><p>To be prepared for war is one of the most effective means of preserving peace.</p><p>---033---</p><p>&quot;In the army, you were the image of indomitable and victorious; in society, you were worthy of being the hero of morality and the public servants... With these wishes and these favors, your commander-in-chief is retiring. The curtain of separation will soon draw aside, and you will forever exit the stage of history.&quot;</p><p>---034---</p><p>i never saw an early,diligent,careful and honest people complain about bad fortune.</p><p>---035---</p><p>Friendship is like the moon, a slow-growing plant.</p><p>---036---</p><p>&quot;Now that I have completed the mission entrusted to me, I feel that I must withdraw from this great stage and return to the solemn state. In its order, I have stood up for a long time. I hereby hand over my commission and resign from all my public offices.&quot;</p><p>---037---</p><p>People&#39;s happiness depends on their mood.</p><p>---038---</p><p>Be courteous to all, but intimate with few, and let those few be well tried before you give them your confidence.</p><p>---039---</p><p>Go to the Lord and look at your lower ten hearts to feel the pain and misfortune of others.</p><p>---040---</p><p>If you cannot apply what you learn from reading, then the books you read are just waste paper.</p>",83)]))}const c=t(n,[["render",p]]);export{f as __pageData,c as default};
